org.apache.tuscany.das.rdb.config
Interface Column

All Known Implementing Classes:
ColumnImpl
public interface Column

A representation of the model object 'Column'.

The following features are supported:

  • Collision
  • Column Type
  • Converter Class Name
  • Generated
  • Name
  • Primary Key
  • Property Name
  • Table
